<app-shell>
  <view class="screen">
    <view class="screen__stack">
      <hero-card
        eyebrow="S02 Login"
        title="先完成登录，再进入自助功能"
        summary="我们会先获取微信登录状态，再用手机号创建学生会话。当前开发联调阶段，手机号授权使用受控表单完成。"
        tone="brand"
      />

      <view wx:if="{{errorMessage}}" class="status-banner status-banner--error">
        {{errorMessage}}
      </view>

      <view wx:if="{{statusMessage}}" class="status-banner status-banner--success">
        {{statusMessage}}
      </view>

      <view class="surface-card surface-card--soft">
        <view class="eyebrow">Step 1</view>
        <view class="section-subtitle">获取微信登录状态</view>
        <view class="body-text">
          点击后会调用 <text class="login-page__inline-code">wx.login</text> 获取本次登录 code。
        </view>
        <view class="button-stack login-page__button-stack">
          <primary-button
            label="{{loginCodeReady ? '重新获取微信登录状态' : '使用微信登录'}}"
            loading="{{wechatLoading}}"
            bind:tap="handleWechatLogin"
          />
        </view>
      </view>

      <view
        class="surface-card surface-card--warm"
        wx:if="{{loginCodeReady}}"
      >
        <view class="eyebrow">Step 2</view>
        <view class="section-subtitle">手机号授权（开发联调模式）</view>
        <view class="body-text">
          为了跑通 MVP 登录链路，请输入本次授权手机号。该手机号仅用于创建校园会话，不会展示给其他学生。
        </view>

        <view class="screen__stack login-page__form-stack">
          <view class="field">
            <view class="field__label">手机号</view>
            <input
              class="field__input"
              placeholder="请输入已授权手机号"
              type="text"
              maxlength="20"
              value="{{form.phoneNumber}}"
              data-field="phoneNumber"
              bindinput="handleInputChange"
            />
            <view class="field__hint">支持 `13812345678` 或 `+8613812345678`。</view>
          </view>

          <view class="field">
            <view class="field__label">学院（可选）</view>
            <input
              class="field__input"
              placeholder="如暂未填写，将使用默认占位"
              maxlength="64"
              value="{{form.collegeName}}"
              data-field="collegeName"
              bindinput="handleInputChange"
            />
          </view>

          <view class="field">
            <view class="field__label">班级（可选）</view>
            <input
              class="field__input"
              placeholder="如暂未填写，将使用默认占位"
              maxlength="64"
              value="{{form.className}}"
              data-field="className"
              bindinput="handleInputChange"
            />
          </view>

          <view wx:if="{{phoneRefused}}" class="status-banner status-banner--warning">
            当前仍停留在登录页。若要进入学生端，请重新完成手机号授权。
          </view>

          <view class="button-stack">
            <primary-button
              label="授权手机号并登录"
              loading="{{loginLoading}}"
              bind:tap="handleWechatSubmit"
            />
            <secondary-button
              label="拒绝手机号授权"
              bind:tap="handlePhoneRefuse"
            />
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view wx:if="{{showDemoEntry}}" class="surface-card surface-card--muted">
        <view class="eyebrow">Demo</view>
        <view class="section-subtitle">开发演示入口</view>
        <view class="body-text">
          仅在后端显式开启演示模式时显示。若同时开启容错模式，登录后可直接配合预置案例完成演示。
        </view>
        <view wx:if="{{demoModeHint}}" class="login-page__demo-hint">
          {{demoModeHint}}
        </view>
        <view class="button-stack login-page__button-stack">
          <secondary-button
            label="使用演示账号进入"
            loading="{{demoLoading}}"
            bind:tap="handleDemoLogin"
          />
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</app-shell>
